OL,13,G0300 World's Most Scenic Railway
OL,14,G     Journeys
OL,15,     FStarting from one of the world's
OL,16,     Fmost remote cities, Walvis Bay, in
OL,17,     FNamibia, we roll 1,500 miles
OL,18,     Fthrough the Kalahari desert to
OL,19,     FPretoria, South Africa's Executive
OL,20,     FCapital.
